  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Secret Alignments track a student’s behavioral patterns &amp grant both advantages and disadvantages.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each student falls into one of five alignments based on choices they make throughout the semester.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Alignments provide small bonuses but also impose secret challenges.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> A student’s final challenge is subtly influenced by their alignment.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: The Five Secret Alignments</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Alignment</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Description</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Bonus</div>",
